  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragons are an absolute myth! Nobody has ever seen any!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's No Dragons is a hidden object game with a selection of 9 locations and random dragons to find for each of them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 9 Different Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 Difficulty Settings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >customizable background colors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > replayable with 20 dragons out of 60 selected for each play </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >special hidden dragons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > hint system </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > zoom </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > achievements</p></li></ul>",
